</p>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Further_reading">Further reading</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Republic_of_Sierra_Leone_Armed_Forces&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10" title="Edit section: Further reading"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<ul><li>Twenty-third Report of the SRSG on UNAMSIL, and Crisis Group Africa Report No. 87, 8 DEcember 2004.</li>
<li>Peter Albrecht and Paul Jackson, <i>Security System Transformation in Sierra Leone, 1997–2007</i>, Global Facilitation Network for Security Sector Reform, accessible at <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.ssrnetwork.net/publications/gfn_ssr_publications.php">GFN-SSR Publications Archives</a> <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20100820083512/http://www.ssrnetwork.net/publications/gfn_ssr_publications.php">Archived</a> 20 August 2010 at the <a href="/wiki/Wayback_Machine" title="Wayback Machine">Wayback Machine</a></li>
